		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well, this is similar to Panic Space on the FDS.<br /><br />It's also similar to a popular game named Deflektor that came out in the '80s on home computers, and later on the GameBoy as &quot;Migrain&quot;.<br /><br />Cool stuff, tho!

		

